                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Nina Campbell, one of England's leading interior designers, reveals the secrets of her unique style and offers invaluable decorator's tips with an inside look at ten of her most inviting and elegant homes:<P>Classic English Style<P>Small but stylish<P>New for old<P>Rooftop drama<P>East meets west<P>A Baronial castle<P>Town and country<P>An English country house<P>A banker's retreat<P>Elegance in miniature</span>
              
